Available Tools: add_to_cart | remove_from_cart | update_quantity | get_cart | apply_coupon | checkout
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "product_id": "string", "quantity": "number", "coupon_code": "string" }
Response Schema: { "cart_id": "string", "items": [{ "product_id": "string", "name": "string", "quantity": "number", "price": "number" }], "total": "number" }
---
Question: Apply the holiday promo code HOLIDAY25 to my bookstore cart.
Call: { "func_call": "apply_coupon", "product_id": "", "quantity": 0, "coupon_code": "HOLIDAY25" }
Response: { "cart_id": "CART-4421", "items": [{ "product_id": "PROD-302", "name": "Mystery Novel Collection", "quantity": 2, "price": 24.99 }], "total": 37.48 }

Question: Try using the outdated coupon code WINTER2022 on my furniture order.
Call: { "func_call": "apply_coupon", "product_id": "", "quantity": 0, "coupon_code": "WINTER2022" }
Response: { "cart_id": "CART-4421", "items": [{ "product_id": "PROD-302", "name": "Mystery Novel Collection", "quantity": 2, "price": 24.99 }], "total": 49.98 }

Question: Finalize the purchase for the current book selection.
Call: { "func_call": "checkout", "product_id": "", "quantity": 0, "coupon_code": "" }
Response: { "cart_id": "CART-4421", "items": [{ "product_id": "PROD-302", "name": "Mystery Novel Collection", "quantity": 2, "price": 24.99 }], "total": 49.98 }

